    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Equity for Disaster Victims Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill assists victims of Superstorm Sandy and other disasters by allowing recipients of specified disaster-assistance loans from the Small Business Administration to repay the loans with disaster-recovery grant funds received&nbsp;under the Community Development Block Grant Program.</p>]]></text>
